332
00:26:16,270 --> 00:26:17,620
Hej!

333
00:26:19,340 --> 00:26:21,210
Tento šialenec...

334
00:26:23,090 --> 00:26:24,940
Tu.

335
00:26:27,260 --> 00:26:29,410
[Manokine]

336
00:26:44,300 --> 00:26:47,210
Hej, kde to je?
Kde si to dal?

337
00:26:51,270 --> 00:26:54,220
- Kde si položil ten balík?
- Vyhodil som ho.

338
00:26:54,340 --> 00:26:55,640
Čo?

339
00:26:55,980 --> 00:26:57,630
Vyhodil som ho.

340
00:26:57,630 --> 00:27:01,890
Varoval som ťa, že ak prídeš neskoro,
uistím sa, že toho budeš ľutovať.

341
00:27:01,890 --> 00:27:04,860
Čo je? To si ho naozaj vyhodil?

342
00:27:05,270 --> 00:27:08,790
Doriti! Bolo to z limitovanej edície.
Kde si to vyhodil?

343
00:27:08,790 --> 00:27:10,510
Kde?

344
00:27:10,820 --> 00:27:15,380
