Radšej by si si mal pohnúť.

345
00:27:16,170 --> 00:27:18,100
Doriti! Ty...

346
00:27:21,360 --> 00:27:23,170
Zastavte! Zastavte!

347
00:27:32,360 --> 00:27:34,670
Bolo to z novej kolekcie.

348
00:27:34,670 --> 00:27:36,160
Dobrá práca.

349
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:38,580
Pozor! Pokloňte sa majsterke!

350
00:27:38,580 --> 00:27:43,330
Ďakujem. Majte sa, dobrá práca.

351
00:27:49,650 --> 00:27:51,960
